title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Ryan Navion - Start the engine
description:
The Ryan Navion has been released earlier this week. Based on the early review where we did hit some challenges starting the engine manually I got some feedback from the developer with the correct steps. In this video I will show you the steps on how to start the engine.

The latest version of the aircraft can be downloaded from flightsim.to:
https://flightsim.to/file/23285/ryan-navion
